1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,780
=Episode 19=

16
00:01:46,239 --> 00:01:47,400
Just as I was about to reach

17
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,920
the peak of my life,

18
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:51,319
the doctor told me

19
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,000
that my wife

20
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:56,400
had cancer.

21
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,400
After knowing that,

22
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,760
I didn't sleep for days.

23
00:02:25,639 --> 00:02:26,879
The view from up here

24
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,479
really looks different.

25
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:33,610
You will get used to it
after seeing it enough.

26
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,159
Because you've attained it,

27
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,039
it doesn't matter anymore.

28
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:47,900
(A lady from a wealthy family fell for a poor student.
We worked overseas and got married.)

29
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:50,919
Why are you mentioning my late wife
in my speech script?

30
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:56,840
Your previous drafts

31
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,280
were written too stiffly.

32
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,719
Mentioning emotions this time

33
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,159
can make you

34
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:02,479
appear more charismatic.

35
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,039
In the future, you will still

36
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,080
need to have

37
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,080
a capable assistant.

38
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:09,159
People like Rao Yuci and Bai Liangliang

39
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,120
won't do.

40
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,639
Only I can.

41
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,199
Misfortunes never come alone.

42
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,840
Along with that,

43
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,000
the other piece of news

44
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,159
was the once-in-a-century
subprime mortgage crisis in America.

45
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:33,520
Wall Street was a complete mess.

46
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,199
I had a few

47
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,520
friends who ran hedge funds.

48
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,740
We agreed to meet on the rooftop.

49
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,560
Then...

50
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,000
I lost my job.

51
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,639
My wife was gravely ill.

52
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,120
Back then, I was just one step away

53
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,039
from following in their footsteps,

54
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,800
leaping down from the top floor

55
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,719
of Morgan Stanley.

56
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,100
Right when I was in my most painful

57
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:57,879
and most desperate moment,

58
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,360
I met the mentor of my life,

59
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,080
Mr. Li Wancheng.

60
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:18,240
Mr. Li found me when Lysen
was at a crossroads,

61
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,079
deciding its future.

62
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,600
He wanted me to lead Lysen

63
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,279
and start a new era.

64
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,199
But I hesitated.

65
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,519
Because...

66
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,399
I couldn't abandon

67
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:34,560
my wife on her sickbed.

68
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,839
It was at that time

69
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,319
that my dying wife said to me,

70
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,600
"Dongchao,

71
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,040
go back.

72
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:45,560
Don't worry about me.

73
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,399
Go pursue your dreams.

74
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:51,600
It's for us, too."

75
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,000
You know

76
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,040
the rest of the story.

77
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,959
We have a new Lysen,

78
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,920
but I wasn't able to

79
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:06,639
accompany my wife

80
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:09,079
through the final stage of her life.

81
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,399
Lysen's prosperity

82
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,480
comes from the sacrifice
of an ordinary woman.

83
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,000
As the great ship of Lysen

84
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:19,079
is about to set sail toward the future,

85
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,439
I will carry my wife's legacy

86
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:23,600
to bring even greater value

87
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,560
to Mr. Li

88
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,879
and all the shareholders!

89
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,879
Finally, I'd like to use a quote

90
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:34,199
from my favorite author,

91
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,279
Herman Melville,

92
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,519
from his book Moby Dick,

93
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:41,820
"The best way to predict the future

94
00:05:43,100 --> 00:05:45,060
is to create it."

95
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,560
The best way to predict the future

96
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,920
is to create it.

97
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,399
Wancheng,

98
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,399
do you believe him?

99
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,519
He told me this story

100
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:13,040
about his wife years ago.

101
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,399
Do you think I believe it?

102
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:16,319
I only believe

103
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,600
in how much profit he can bring me.

104
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:23,360
Follow for more content.

105
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:23,720
Hello,

106
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,839
I am Qi.

107
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,600
The acquisition of Bosi by Lysen
has officially kicked off.

108
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:28,759
Lysen Group

109
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:30,120
is heavily buying Bosi shares

110
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,519
listed in Hong Kong, China.

111
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,959
Unexpectedly, Yinyu Technology

112
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:34,560
suddenly showed up,

113
00:06:34,879 --> 00:06:35,959
spending over a billion yuan

114
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,800
to snatch a 6 percent stake.

115
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:40,360
Xian Pengyu, the shareholder
behind Yinyu Technology,

116
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,519
has entered the public eye.

117
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:43,120
And Xian Pengyu's mother

118
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:45,000
is the head of Yuanjian Group,

119
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,800
Xin Shaonan.

120
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:49,639
Whether Yinyu Technology's intervention
was at the instruction of Xin Shaonan

121
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,290
has sparked speculation
from all sectors.

122
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,199
You've done very well.

123
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,879
But this stock price isn't high enough.

124
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:57,790
We need to add more fuel to the fire.

125
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,160
Don't worry, Grandmother.

126
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:02,480
I will handle this matter well.

127
00:07:11,850 --> 00:07:13,120
Mr. Jiang, you wanted to see me?

128
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,639
Has Rao Yuci

129
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:18,000
already been discharged?

130
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:24,160
I haven't mentioned
this person for a long time.

131
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:26,000
Did you all think

132
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,120
that I'd forgotten about her?

133
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,920
Rao Yuci is discharged.

134
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,519
Where do you think

135
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:34,720
she will go next?

136
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,879
I heard

137
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:42,920
that Yu Peidong went to see

138
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,120
Rao Yuci a while ago.

139
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,759
As for exactly what was said,

140
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:47,560
I'm sure you

141
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:49,160
know better than I do.

142
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:51,959
Mr. Jiang,

143
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:54,519
Mr. Yu and Rao Yuci

144
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:55,839
are just colleagues.

145
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,199
I think their meeting

146
00:07:58,279 --> 00:07:59,399
was just a matter of

147
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:01,079
colleagues looking out for each other.

148
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,240
Three months ago,

149
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:08,240
Rao Yuci left as if leaving
everything in others' hands.

150
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,800
But

151
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,319
I still haven't opened

152
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,839
her resignation letter to this day.

153
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,800
Do you know why?

154
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:20,120
Because I was certain

155
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,759
that she would come back.

156
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,319
Who wouldn't want

157
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,519
a talent like her,

158
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:28,720
who is thorough

159
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,280
and ruthless even with herself?

160
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,480
But Ms. Ren,

161
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,919
if a talent like this

162
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,799
falls into the hands of a rival,

163
00:08:39,519 --> 00:08:40,360
they will surely

164
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,279
become a sharp blade

165
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,279
aimed at our Lysen.

166
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,279
The acquisition

167
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,879
has reached its most critical point.

168
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,000
I don't want

169
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,600
any complications

170
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,799
to arise at a time like this.

171
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,919
Do you understand?

172
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,559
I understand, Mr. Jiang.

173
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,320
You seem to have lost weight.

174
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,600
I was just discharged.

175
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:10,200
You can lose weight in the hospital?

176
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,720
Sign me up for a few days.

177
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,519
Sure.

178
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,759
Don't blame me for this.

179
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:20,360
Something big happened at Lysen lately,

180
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:22,000
and I didn't dare tell you.

181
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:25,730
Over the last three months,

182
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,600
with the stock numbers rising one by one,

183
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:30,399
Jiang Dongchao has gone crazy.

184
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:32,519
He's going all out to acquire Bosi.

185
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,679
To consolidate funds,

186
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,240
all other company projects

187
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,200
have been sidelined,

188
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:40,399
including green building materials
and the Snack Street.

189
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:45,240
And coincidentally,

190
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,840
Xian Pengyu also chose this time
to shut down the Snack Street.

191
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:50,879
I've been to the leasing office

192
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:52,320
at Yinyu Technology several times.

193
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,679
Their attitude is very firm.

194
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:58,279
They just won't say the real reason
for closing the Snack Street.

195
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:22,580
(Rao Yuci)

196
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:28,900
(Xian Pengyu)

197
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,679
(Rao Yuci)
(Mr. Pengyu, I need to see you.)

198
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,520
(The Snack Street was shut down.)

199
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:57,360
(Please give me an explanation.)

200
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,399
(National Enterprise Credit Information Publicity System)
I've cleared it up.

201
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,690
The registered address
of Yinyu Technology

202
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:06,500
is one of Xian Pengyu's
commercial buildings.

203
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,320
This building

204
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,840
hasn't been up for lease for a year.

205
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,879
It's likely just a front.

206
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,990
As for the other shareholders
of Yinyu Technology,

207
00:11:14,279 --> 00:11:15,639
one is named Xu Ning.

208
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,639
The others have family backgrounds
in the insurance industry.

209
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:19,720
They all

210
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,000
work for Xian Pengyu.

211
00:11:21,279 --> 00:11:22,360
Xu Ning's father

212
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,480
has a relationship with you.

213
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:25,560
I don't think it
would be hard to get him to stop.

214
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,879
But Xian Pengyu...

215
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:32,930
Could it be that Xin Shaonan
is pulling the strings from behind?

216
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:36,919
Just a bunch of punks.

217
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:41,679
Yuanjian has never done any

218
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:43,159
real estate-related projects.

219
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,240
Why would Xian Pengyu

220
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,879
rashly jump

221
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:48,960
into Bosi?

222
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,679
Their target isn't Bosi.

223
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,159
It's me.

224
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:05,140
(Eighteen years ago)

225
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,399
Today,

226
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:16,039
we are here to mourn and remember

227
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:18,720
my husband, Xian Donghai.

228
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:21,000
His passing

229
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,320
has taken away

230
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,799
the most important part of my life.

231
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,360
My heart is filled with

232
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,399
endless longing and pain.

233
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:30,080
Donghai

234
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,960
was a diligent and persistent man.

235
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,240
In his career...

236
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,480
Shaonan.

237
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,879
Shaonan, my condolences.

238
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,399
Get out.

239
00:12:58,919 --> 00:13:00,639
You're not welcome here.

240
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:13,960
Dear friends and family,

241
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:15,960
one year ago,

242
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,840
Yuanjian was acquiring Yinghuo Shipping,

243
00:13:18,279 --> 00:13:20,440
so Donghai raised funds from the market

244
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,799
and took on many VAM agreements.

245
00:13:24,039 --> 00:13:24,840
There was someone

246
00:13:25,759 --> 00:13:27,120
who, as Donghai's old classmate

247
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,279
and good friend,

248
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:31,559
knew all the details
of those agreements.

249
00:13:33,519 --> 00:13:36,080
He secretly used Xiongshi Fund

250
00:13:36,279 --> 00:13:38,039
to target Yinghuo Shipping,

251
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:40,840
causing Yuanjian's acquisition to fail.

252
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,639
The person directly responsible

253
00:13:43,639 --> 00:13:44,960
for Donghai's death

254
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:47,919
is the man standing before you,

255
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,200
Jiang Dongchao.

256
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,679
Yuci, you don't need to worry about us.

257
00:14:40,679 --> 00:14:41,960
We're doing quite well.

258
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,440
Where's Nuan's father?

259
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:46,470
There's a construction site nearby.

260
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,559
He went there to help out.

261
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,799
And Nuan?

262
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:50,720
Right now, neither of us

263
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,799
can look after her.

264
00:14:52,399 --> 00:14:53,440
We had to send her back

265
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,919
to her grandmother's in the country.

266
00:14:55,279 --> 00:14:56,520
During winter or summer break,

267
00:14:56,639 --> 00:14:58,159
we'll bring her back.

268
00:15:00,799 --> 00:15:01,600
Look.

269
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,360
This is the compensation agreement

270
00:15:03,639 --> 00:15:05,279
given to all the vendors

271
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:06,360
by the building management.

272
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,080
The Snack Street was doing so well.

273
00:15:09,279 --> 00:15:10,879
How could it just close like that?

274
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:14,380
(Compensation Agreement)

275
00:15:15,100 --> 00:15:17,289
(Party A confirms failure
to fulfill obligations under Article 7)

276
00:15:17,290 --> 00:15:19,940
(Party A acknowledges that its breach of contract
has caused direct and indirect losses to Party B)

277
00:15:42,039 --> 00:15:43,000
Welcome

278
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:46,799
to the Linwei Alley in our memories.

279
00:15:47,679 --> 00:15:48,480
Welcome.

280
00:15:48,679 --> 00:15:49,960
Welcome!

281
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:53,879
Come, come.

282
00:15:53,879 --> 00:15:55,600
Try the new items at our shop.

283
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,720
Thanks a lot.

284
00:15:56,759 --> 00:15:58,360
Osmanthus mixed fruit bowl.

285
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:00,000
Feel free to give more feedback.

286
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:19,399
We negotiated partnerships

287
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,639
with those green building
materials companies

288
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:23,200
one by one with great effort.

289
00:16:23,890 --> 00:16:25,279
With one word from Jiang Dongchao,

290
00:16:25,279 --> 00:16:26,399
they have to stop production.

291
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:27,960
Those materials

292
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,600
were already on the production line.

293
00:16:30,399 --> 00:16:31,720
Leaving them halfway like this,

294
00:16:31,919 --> 00:16:33,480
you're just leaving them to rot, no?

295
00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:44,639
The vendors from the Snack Street
are now setting up stalls everywhere.

296
00:16:45,399 --> 00:16:46,279
They went to negotiate

297
00:16:46,279 --> 00:16:47,360
with the Yinyu Technology
leasing office,

298
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,440
(Compensation Agreement)

299
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,800
but the other side gave no reason.

300
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,639
The compensation is the reason.

301
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:53,799
(Compensation Agreement. Party A:
Shanghai Yinyu Technology Co., Ltd.)

302
00:16:53,799 --> 00:16:54,679
So do you think

303
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:56,559
it has anything to do with me?

304
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,840
Whether it has anything
to do with you or not, Yuci,

305
00:17:02,759 --> 00:17:04,119
let's not get involved anymore.

306
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:05,759
We have already
done our best to help them.

307
00:17:05,759 --> 00:17:07,119
What do you mean you did your best?

308
00:17:08,519 --> 00:17:09,319
We don't even know

309
00:17:09,319 --> 00:17:10,359
what happened.

310
00:17:13,519 --> 00:17:15,599
Both of these things
started because of me.

311
00:17:16,599 --> 00:17:18,119
I can't just ignore them.

312
00:17:25,799 --> 00:17:26,599
Yuci.

313
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:31,559
After your accident,

314
00:17:33,119 --> 00:17:34,200
I've repeatedly replayed

315
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,400
every word we've said

316
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,920
since the day we met.

317
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:39,799
I know you're holding onto

318
00:17:39,799 --> 00:17:40,920
your idealism.

319
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:42,480
When you were doing those things,

320
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,160
I felt like

321
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,119
you were glowing,

322
00:17:44,119 --> 00:17:45,039
and it drew me to you.

323
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,599
I also really hoped

324
00:17:48,119 --> 00:17:48,799
that I could

325
00:17:48,799 --> 00:17:52,160
defend this pure land together with you
through my own efforts.

326
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,359
But when you were lying there,
I got scared.

327
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,759
I was truly terrified.

328
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:19,180
(Resuscitation Area)

329
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,200
Yuci,

330
00:18:22,279 --> 00:18:23,680
can you hear me?

331
00:18:25,839 --> 00:18:27,039
I know you're very tired,

332
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,039
but promise me

333
00:18:29,039 --> 00:18:30,519
that you must wake up, okay?

334
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:33,519
Promise me.

335
00:18:37,599 --> 00:18:39,000
I'm afraid I'll lose you.

336
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:42,480
I'm afraid someone will hurt you again.

337
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:46,119
You can say I'm selfish.

338
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:48,039
You can say I'm small-minded.

339
00:18:48,039 --> 00:18:48,920
That's fine.

340
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,039
I don't want you

341
00:18:51,039 --> 00:18:52,400
to have any more accidents.

342
00:19:10,519 --> 00:19:11,599
Thank you, Chen Mo.

343
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:15,200
Do you still remember
the letter I left for you

344
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,200
before I went to see Bai Muran?

345
00:19:18,519 --> 00:19:19,359
Mr. Chen,

346
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:21,039
this is the letter Yuci left for you.

347
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:29,039
(Chen Mo.)

348
00:19:30,799 --> 00:19:31,480
(It's my turn)

349
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:32,920
(to write a letter to you.)

350
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:37,279
(Our story ends here.)

351
00:19:37,599 --> 00:19:38,839
(Don't let it continue.)

352
00:19:41,839 --> 00:19:42,720
(A few years ago,)

353
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,680
(everyone I loved
distanced themselves from me.)

354
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:46,690
It's useless telling you.

355
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:48,640
(The people I cared about most)

356
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:50,400
Dear,

357
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,559
(all betrayed me.)

358
00:19:51,559 --> 00:19:52,839
just wait to die.

359
00:19:58,279 --> 00:19:59,640
(I thought every day,)

360
00:20:01,319 --> 00:20:02,920
(what exactly did I do wrong?)

361
00:20:05,279 --> 00:20:05,960
(In my mind,)

362
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:08,480
(all hope for this world
had completely vanished.)

363
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,640
(I was left with only one strength,)

364
00:20:13,319 --> 00:20:14,400
(which is obsession.)

365
00:20:15,839 --> 00:20:17,359
(So, relying on that obsession,)

366
00:20:18,519 --> 00:20:19,599
(I bit by bit became)

367
00:20:19,599 --> 00:20:21,119
(the way I am now.)

368
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:24,160
(I thought I could train myself)

369
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,400
(to be like those people,)

370
00:20:25,839 --> 00:20:27,359
(where besides hatred, I wouldn't have)

371
00:20:27,359 --> 00:20:28,720
(any other emotions anymore.)

372
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,519
(But then you appeared.)

373
00:20:34,519 --> 00:20:37,220
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

374
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:40,580
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

375
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:41,920
After walking with
your head down for so long,

376
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:42,799
you should learn

377
00:20:44,319 --> 00:20:45,559
to look up from time to time

378
00:20:45,559 --> 00:20:46,720
at this different world.

379
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,039
Perhaps

380
00:20:50,279 --> 00:20:51,160
it isn't as bad

381
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,079
as we imagined.

382
00:20:52,599 --> 00:20:54,079
Remember what I said?

383
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:57,359
I'm used to being alone.

384
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:00,880
That's because on this path,

385
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:04,519
I am destined to be alone.

386
00:21:05,380 --> 00:21:06,220
(Chen Mo)

387
00:21:07,119 --> 00:21:08,079
(Because once I have)

388
00:21:08,079 --> 00:21:09,359
(someone I care about again,)

389
00:21:11,799 --> 00:21:13,799
(I will have a weakness
that can destroy me.)

390
00:21:13,799 --> 00:21:15,820
(Goodbye. From Rao Yuci)

391
00:21:16,359 --> 00:21:17,559
(So there are some things)

392
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,279
(I must finish on my own.)

393
00:21:22,799 --> 00:21:24,000
(I will remember)

394
00:21:25,759 --> 00:21:27,200
(everything different)

395
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:30,160
(that you brought to me.)

396
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:35,100
♪This pathetic kindness♪

397
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,480
It will all pass.

398
00:21:38,820 --> 00:21:40,420
(Nuan)

399
00:21:40,420 --> 00:21:47,220
♪When the cold wind passes
it takes the past away♪

400
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,599
But your plan

401
00:21:48,599 --> 00:21:49,799
is already complete.

402
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:55,079
No, it's not fully finished yet.

403
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:07,519
(I must make
the lights of the Snack Street)

404
00:22:08,599 --> 00:22:09,799
(shine again.)

405
00:22:11,519 --> 00:22:12,400
(I believe)

406
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:15,079
(I can do all of this.)

407
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:31,519
(Rongguangli, 24/7 Convenience Store)

408
00:22:31,519 --> 00:22:32,319
Little Genius,

409
00:22:32,599 --> 00:22:33,680
let's meet.

410
00:22:57,660 --> 00:23:00,500
(Ertou Restaurant)

411
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,519
Hello.

412
00:23:20,860 --> 00:23:22,920
I heard you still want
to reopen the Snack Street.

413
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:24,279
Little Genius,

414
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:26,079
you're persistent.

415
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:29,600
The Snack Street won't hinder
your acquisition of Bosi's equity,

416
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,000
unless someone

417
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:33,039
offered you some benefit

418
00:23:33,559 --> 00:23:34,279
or reached

419
00:23:34,279 --> 00:23:35,480
an agreement with you.

420
00:23:41,079 --> 00:23:41,880
Smart.

421
00:23:43,279 --> 00:23:44,359
I did indeed

422
00:23:44,759 --> 00:23:46,079
promise someone else first.

423
00:23:46,759 --> 00:23:47,559
So,

424
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:49,680
sorry.

425
00:23:50,079 --> 00:23:51,440
I'm very clear about the story

426
00:23:51,559 --> 00:23:52,519
of you and your father.

427
00:23:53,079 --> 00:23:54,480
Many people are very clear about it.

428
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:56,119
But always

429
00:23:56,119 --> 00:23:57,759
living inside your own story

430
00:23:58,580 --> 00:24:00,240
makes it very likely
you'll lose your way

431
00:24:01,039 --> 00:24:01,880
or perhaps

432
00:24:03,580 --> 00:24:05,500
be manipulated
by someone with hidden motives.

433
00:24:08,799 --> 00:24:09,960
This is a hunting ground.

434
00:24:10,079 --> 00:24:12,720
If I want to enter the field,
I must get a ticket.

435
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:13,880
As for whether you and I

436
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:16,079
can still sit at the same table
in the future,

437
00:24:16,079 --> 00:24:17,519
it depends on whether
Jiang Dongchao or I

438
00:24:17,519 --> 00:24:18,839
will be the final winner.

439
00:24:19,319 --> 00:24:20,319
I'm going into

440
00:24:20,440 --> 00:24:21,759
this hunting ground.

441
00:24:22,039 --> 00:24:22,799
And Rao Yuci,

442
00:24:22,799 --> 00:24:24,039
I can tell you clearly,

443
00:24:24,039 --> 00:24:26,160
don't talk to me
about the Snack Street anymore.

444
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,279
Because I've already decided.

445
00:24:27,279 --> 00:24:29,839
No matter how angry you are,
you're just a "good person".

446
00:24:29,839 --> 00:24:31,400
A good person has no hidden cards,

447
00:24:31,400 --> 00:24:32,640
only weaknesses.

448
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,559
And with weaknesses,

449
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,720
you're bound to lose.

450
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:36,480
By helping you shut down
the entire Snack Street,

451
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:38,039
I'm helping you remove a weakness.

452
00:24:38,039 --> 00:24:39,599
In that sense, it's for your own good.

453
00:24:39,599 --> 00:24:40,359
So,

454
00:24:41,039 --> 00:24:42,079
don't thank me.

455
00:24:42,119 --> 00:24:43,039
Then who exactly

456
00:24:43,039 --> 00:24:44,119
did you make a deal with?

457
00:24:52,599 --> 00:24:53,599
No comment.

458
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:55,799
Just consider me a bad person.

459
00:24:55,799 --> 00:24:57,119
I think you're a good person.

460
00:24:59,839 --> 00:25:01,240
Becoming a bad person is easy,

461
00:25:02,319 --> 00:25:03,759
but admitting you're a good person

462
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:06,440
seems very hard for you.

463
00:25:06,599 --> 00:25:09,680
And besides, who says good people
don't have hidden cards?

464
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:55,599
Let's have a drink.

465
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:11,680
(One month ago)
Three, two, one!

466
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:12,799
Cheers!

467
00:26:13,599 --> 00:26:14,400
Alright.

468
00:26:16,359 --> 00:26:17,160
It's here.

469
00:26:17,170 --> 00:26:18,200
Here's your copper hot pot.

470
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,390
Careful now, don't get burned.

471
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:21,960
Come...

472
00:26:22,060 --> 00:26:26,660
(Shengnan Restaurant)

473
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:37,599
It's been a while.

474
00:26:39,079 --> 00:26:40,160
I was quite surprised

475
00:26:40,319 --> 00:26:41,640
that you'd call me.

476
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:43,660
After disappearing for so long,

477
00:26:43,799 --> 00:26:44,839
you've finally surfaced.

478
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,200
Nice new haircut.

479
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,000
When a beast is wounded,

480
00:26:53,039 --> 00:26:54,640
it also needs time to recover.

481
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,079
I know your story,

482
00:26:59,839 --> 00:27:00,519
and I know

483
00:27:00,519 --> 00:27:01,880
you have your own plan.

484
00:27:02,759 --> 00:27:03,960
But relying solely

485
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,000
on the anger in that story

486
00:27:05,839 --> 00:27:07,119
probably won't be enough.

487
00:27:09,319 --> 00:27:10,319
I have a question.

488
00:27:11,759 --> 00:27:12,799
Over the past year,

489
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,200
you had several opportunities

490
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,279
to strike at Lysen.

491
00:27:16,599 --> 00:27:18,039
Why did you detour to Bosi?

492
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:20,839
Because Lysen

493
00:27:20,839 --> 00:27:22,319
doesn't belong to Jiang Dongchao.

494
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:24,160
If I moved against Lysen,

495
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,240
no one would help me,

496
00:27:25,300 --> 00:27:26,960
and the chances
of winning would be slim.

497
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,680
But Bosi is different.

498
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:30,599
It's a prize.

499
00:27:31,359 --> 00:27:32,480
Who wouldn't want it?

500
00:27:34,759 --> 00:27:35,799
I've waited so long,

501
00:27:36,359 --> 00:27:37,079
and finally

502
00:27:37,079 --> 00:27:38,640
Jiang Dongchao stepped in himself.

503
00:27:40,039 --> 00:27:41,599
By acquiring Bosi Fund,

504
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,640
he has to assume joint liability.

505
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:46,279
Just like my father back then.

506
00:27:47,359 --> 00:27:49,039
Where my father fell years ago,

507
00:27:49,519 --> 00:27:51,440
I'll make Jiang Dongchao fall

508
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:52,920
in exactly the same way.

509
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,000
You're not wrong.

510
00:27:58,160 --> 00:27:59,039
If you want revenge,

511
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:01,240
anger alone isn't enough.

512
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:03,319
You must endure,

513
00:28:03,839 --> 00:28:04,880
plan ahead,

514
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,559
and stare down your opponent

515
00:28:06,839 --> 00:28:08,200
like a beast.

516
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:09,759
When he thinks

517
00:28:09,759 --> 00:28:11,440
the easy prize

518
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:12,160
is about to reach

519
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,160
his mouth,

520
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,720
you snatch it away.

521
00:28:16,039 --> 00:28:18,240
That will be much more satisfying

522
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,160
and much more delicious.

523
00:28:28,319 --> 00:28:28,960
Alright,

524
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:31,079
I've finished my part.

525
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:32,279
Your turn.

526
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,240
You didn't come to me

527
00:28:34,279 --> 00:28:35,279
just for revenge

528
00:28:35,279 --> 00:28:36,279
against Jiang Dongchao

529
00:28:36,279 --> 00:28:38,039
for kicking you out of Lysen, right?

530
00:28:39,079 --> 00:28:41,079
Jiang Dongchao removed me from Lysen,

531
00:28:41,079 --> 00:28:42,599
and I will settle that debt.

532
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:46,039
I've worked with Jiang Dongchao
for so many years,

533
00:28:46,039 --> 00:28:47,359
so I know him very well.

534
00:28:48,559 --> 00:28:50,920
If we join forces,
our odds of winning are fifty-fifty.

535
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,240
Even if Jiang Dongchao's

536
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,039
share in Bosi exceeds yours,

537
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:56,880
I still have

538
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:59,319
ten percent of Baiye.

539
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:03,519
That ten percent, plus yours,

540
00:29:03,799 --> 00:29:05,839
will be our final weapon
to turn the tide.

541
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:07,000
But the premise is,

542
00:29:07,119 --> 00:29:08,799
your share cannot let Jiang Dongchao

543
00:29:08,799 --> 00:29:10,200
pull too far ahead.

544
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,319
We've known each other for years.

545
00:29:13,319 --> 00:29:13,960
I think I have

546
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:14,720
a fairly good

547
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,640
understanding of you.

548
00:29:15,640 --> 00:29:15,920
You

549
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,599
never negotiate

550
00:29:17,599 --> 00:29:18,839
a deal without conditions.

551
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:20,279
So tell me.

552
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:21,880
What's the condition?

553
00:29:37,799 --> 00:29:39,680
I want you
to shut this place down entirely.

554
00:29:56,319 --> 00:29:57,799
Miss Rao, this way please.

555
00:30:15,119 --> 00:30:15,920
Have a seat.

556
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:34,160
Chairman will be here shortly.

557
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,160
Please wait a moment.

558
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:36,200
Thank you.

559
00:30:49,420 --> 00:30:52,540
(Xin Shaonan,
Chairman of Yuanjian Group)

560
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,039
Rao Yuci,

561
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:56,440
hello.

562
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,000
I'm Xin Shaonan.

563
00:30:59,559 --> 00:31:00,480
Hello, Ms. Xin.

564
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:02,880
Have a seat.

565
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,039
Care for a drink?

566
00:31:12,519 --> 00:31:13,440
Come on, cheers.

567
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:25,000
I'm curious.

568
00:31:25,839 --> 00:31:28,039
You and I have never worked together.

569
00:31:28,119 --> 00:31:29,559
Why did you come to see me today?

570
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:31,559
Well,

571
00:31:31,559 --> 00:31:32,799
communication with Mr. Pengyu

572
00:31:32,799 --> 00:31:33,839
hasn't been very smooth.

573
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:35,119
So I've come

574
00:31:35,599 --> 00:31:36,759
to see you.

575
00:31:40,119 --> 00:31:41,559
You're a straightforward person,

576
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:43,200
so I'll just be blunt.

577
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:45,480
I've heard something

578
00:31:45,599 --> 00:31:47,960
about the Linwei Alley
Snack Street Renewal Plan

579
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:49,319
you were working on with Pengyu.

580
00:31:49,599 --> 00:31:52,359
Recently, he quietly
closed down the Snack Street.

581
00:31:53,279 --> 00:31:54,279
So today,

582
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,240
you're not here to find me.

583
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:57,640
You're here to beg me.

584
00:32:01,799 --> 00:32:02,799
Ms. Xin, it seems

585
00:32:04,839 --> 00:32:06,759
that you are very clear about everything.

586
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,759
During the three months
I was hospitalized,

587
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:13,640
Mr. Jiang prepared to acquire Bosi.

588
00:32:14,759 --> 00:32:16,480
He even used all of his personal assets

589
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:17,359
as collateral

590
00:32:18,799 --> 00:32:20,480
to assume all joint liabilities.

591
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:24,799
Mr. Jiang seems determined to win.

592
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,440
But he seems

593
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,799
to have overlooked

594
00:32:28,839 --> 00:32:30,920
some very important
shifts in the market,

595
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:33,240
like Yinyu Technology.

596
00:32:34,079 --> 00:32:34,880
Yes.

597
00:32:35,839 --> 00:32:37,559
Pengyu intends
to deal with Jiang Dongchao.

598
00:32:39,519 --> 00:32:42,759
Rao Yuci, you're not the only one
who can do background checks.

599
00:32:44,559 --> 00:32:45,680
When you were young,

600
00:32:46,359 --> 00:32:48,279
you were called a math genius.

601
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:53,319
(Graduation Thesis Defense,
Respondent: Rao Yuci)

602
00:32:53,319 --> 00:32:54,599
After graduating from university,

603
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,079
you founded Chuxia.

604
00:32:56,359 --> 00:32:56,920
Come.

605
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,240
One, two, three, shout "Chuxia."

606
00:32:58,240 --> 00:33:00,920
- Chuxia!
- Chuxia!

607
00:33:01,519 --> 00:33:03,039
Three years ago, because Lysen

608
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:04,720
acquired Chuxia,

609
00:33:05,079 --> 00:33:07,200
(She sold the company to Lysen at 26)
your best friend Bai Liangliang,

610
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:09,200
boyfriend Bai Muran,

611
00:33:09,519 --> 00:33:11,640
and business partner Li Mingxuan

612
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:14,079
teamed up to send you

613
00:33:14,079 --> 00:33:15,440
to the Xinkang Treatment Center.

614
00:33:18,519 --> 00:33:19,480
After you were released,

615
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,640
you joined Lysen.

616
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:23,920
Shortly after,

617
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:25,799
Bai Liangliang left Lysen.

618
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:31,920
Three months ago,

619
00:33:32,599 --> 00:33:34,440
Bai Muran stabbed you

620
00:33:37,079 --> 00:33:38,160
and committed suicide.

621
00:33:40,300 --> 00:33:42,279
So you've just been
discharged from the hospital.

622
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:46,279
These things about me

623
00:33:47,559 --> 00:33:48,920
are not exactly secrets.

624
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:52,519
I'm sure you are well aware.

625
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:54,480
Mr. Pengyu's

626
00:33:54,559 --> 00:33:56,279
move against Mr. Jiang this time

627
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:59,680
is not just
a simple business competition.

628
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:01,839
He wants to avenge his father.

629
00:34:03,599 --> 00:34:04,880
But these matters

630
00:34:05,359 --> 00:34:07,000
have nothing to do
with the Snack Street.

631
00:34:07,759 --> 00:34:08,800
They are just

632
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,960
some ordinary people
trying to make a living.

633
00:34:14,239 --> 00:34:15,360
I hope you

634
00:34:16,159 --> 00:34:19,119
can persuade Mr. Pengyu
to reopen the Snack Street, Ms. Xin.

635
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:26,320
The word on the street

636
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:27,800
is that he and I don't get along.

637
00:34:28,679 --> 00:34:30,519
I think you're aware of that.

638
00:34:31,079 --> 00:34:31,920
Therefore,

639
00:34:32,239 --> 00:34:34,719
whatever he does is his choice.

640
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:36,079
I have no right to interfere.

641
00:34:37,519 --> 00:34:39,360
I'm sorry, I can't help you.

642
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:43,440
What if

643
00:34:45,119 --> 00:34:47,119
someone is using Mr. Pengyu

644
00:34:47,119 --> 00:34:48,519
by closing the Snack Street

645
00:34:49,199 --> 00:34:50,599
to achieve their own

646
00:34:50,599 --> 00:34:51,400
personal vendetta?

647
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:54,679
I will pass on

648
00:34:54,719 --> 00:34:55,880
what you've said to him.

649
00:35:04,119 --> 00:35:04,920
Thank you.

650
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:06,400
I hope

651
00:35:07,690 --> 00:35:09,199
we won't become enemies in the future.

652
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:11,280
Miss Rao,

653
00:35:12,199 --> 00:35:13,599
whether you believe it or not,

654
00:35:14,199 --> 00:35:15,920
we have never been enemies.

655
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,639
Let's just wait and see

656
00:35:18,639 --> 00:35:20,119
how the rest of our story unfolds.

657
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:35,280
Yu.

658
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,000
Morning.

659
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,440
Yu.

660
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:37,079
Morning.

661
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:38,639
Morning.

662
00:35:39,039 --> 00:35:39,840
Yu.

663
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:42,940
(Yinyu Technology)

664
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:45,639
What are you all standing around for?

665
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:46,760
Are you posing?

666
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:56,280
He's here?

667
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:03,920
You guys head out first.

668
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:15,400
Life is truly full of surprises.

669
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,199
Long time no see.

670
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:20,639
Mr. Jiang.

671
00:36:32,199 --> 00:36:33,000
Pengyu.

672
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:34,840
It's been a while.

673
00:36:52,039 --> 00:36:53,559
You really are Donghai's son.

674
00:37:02,100 --> 00:37:05,800
=Episode 19=
(Ticket)

675
00:37:06,501 --> 00:37:08,941
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

676
00:37:08,941 --> 00:37:15,141
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

677
00:37:15,901 --> 00:37:19,101
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

678
00:37:19,101 --> 00:37:23,621
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

679
00:37:23,621 --> 00:37:31,141
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

680
00:37:31,141 --> 00:37:35,061
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

681
00:37:35,061 --> 00:37:39,101
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

682
00:37:39,101 --> 00:37:42,621
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

683
00:37:42,621 --> 00:37:46,581
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

684
00:37:46,581 --> 00:37:50,741
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

685
00:37:50,741 --> 00:37:54,941
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

686
00:37:54,941 --> 00:37:58,741
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

687
00:37:58,741 --> 00:38:02,821
♪Keep walking through the light♪

688
00:38:02,821 --> 00:38:07,021
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

689
00:38:07,021 --> 00:38:13,341
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

690
00:38:30,461 --> 00:38:37,101
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

691
00:38:37,101 --> 00:38:40,941
♪An apology that came too late♪

692
00:38:40,941 --> 00:38:45,581
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

693
00:38:45,661 --> 00:38:53,061
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

694
00:38:53,061 --> 00:38:57,141
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

695
00:38:57,141 --> 00:39:01,221
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

696
00:39:01,221 --> 00:39:05,221
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

697
00:39:05,221 --> 00:39:08,981
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

698
00:39:08,981 --> 00:39:13,181
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

699
00:39:13,181 --> 00:39:17,341
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

700
00:39:17,341 --> 00:39:21,061
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

701
00:39:21,061 --> 00:39:25,101
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

702
00:39:25,101 --> 00:39:29,141
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

703
00:39:29,141 --> 00:39:35,341
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
